1.0 StructureDefinition-au-primarycarecomposition

AU Primary Care Composition Profile [FMM Level 0]

This profile defines a composition structure that includes core localisation concepts for use in an Australian primary care practice-to-practice record transfer context.

Example thanks to Best Practice and Jim Steel .. not yet checked for conformance to this IG

​Compositon 0

1.0.1 Formal Views of Profile Content

The official URL for this profile is: 

https://aehrc.com/fhir/StructureDefinition/AUPrimaryCareComposition

This profile defines a composition structure that includes core localisation concepts for use in an Australian primary care practice-to-practice record transfer context.

This profile builds on AUBaseComposition.

This profile was published on Wed Nov 06 10:56:59 AEST 2019 as a draft by null.
